    持续集成打包时报错Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-surefire-plugin:2.21.0:test我在devops环境下打包时报错[ERROR] Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-surefire-plugin:2.21.0:test (default-test) on project erp: There are test failures.改正方法：在pom的build部分加           
  <plugin>
				<groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
				<artifactId>maven-surefire-plugin</artifactId>
				<configuration>
					<skipTests>true</skipTests>
				</configuration>
			</plugin>--------------------- 作者：东坡子 来源：CSDN 原文：https://blog.csdn.net/wshicainiao/article/details/86480139 版权声明：本文为博主原创文章，转载请附上博文链接！






